00:39:46.270 --> 00:39:47.830
Who has fur? Beard?

00:39:48.280 --> 00:39:49.250
[Very good!]

00:39:49.250 --> 00:39:50.290
[Give it to me!]

00:39:50.660 --> 00:39:50.730
[She really took out the fur...?]

00:39:50.730 --> 00:39:52.160
OK.

00:39:52.900 --> 00:39:54.260
[No one can recognize me this way!]

00:39:54.770 --> 00:39:55.480
[Give it to me!]
[Answer: Whitebeard Lee Sooji]

00:39:55.480 --> 00:39:56.270
Not bad.

00:39:59.230 --> 00:39:59.630
It's very precious.

00:39:59.630 --> 00:40:00.150
[Open]

00:40:00.150 --> 00:40:01.110
[Can't recognize me, can you?]

00:40:01.110 --> 00:40:01.930
It's very precious.

00:40:01.930 --> 00:40:04.960
[Answer: Lee Sooji holding a fan]

00:40:05.240 --> 00:40:06.840
[(Manager:) I'm so nervous.]

00:40:07.080 --> 00:40:08.320
[(Manager:) I'm really nervous.]

00:40:08.320 --> 00:40:09.130
No way. Who can recognize me like this?

00:40:09.130 --> 00:40:10.520
[Cannot understand]

00:40:10.790 --> 00:40:10.800
[+props]

00:40:10.800 --> 00:40:12.570
Will anyone recognize me?

00:40:12.700 --> 00:40:13.750
[Answer: Lee Sooji wearing a helmet.]

00:40:13.750 --> 00:40:15.880
I think you'll be recognized right away.

00:40:15.880 --> 00:40:17.790
[(Manager:) Walk outside for 5 minutes.]

00:40:17.790 --> 00:40:19.010
Let’s see if people recognize you.

00:40:19.010 --> 00:40:19.110
[Proposing a popularity test]

00:40:19.110 --> 00:40:20.110
Let's test it out.

00:40:20.160 --> 00:40:21.550
Rehearsal. Rehearsal.

00:40:22.330 --> 00:40:26.870
[Lee Sooji: I'll say hi
to the office guys first.]

00:40:27.610 --> 00:40:29.420
[Who am I?]

00:40:29.720 --> 00:40:31.450
[Oh? Lee Sooji?]

00:40:31.770 --> 00:40:33.270
[Immediately recognized]

00:40:33.270 --> 00:40:35.060
Thank you.

00:40:37.430 --> 00:40:38.430
[Oh?]

00:40:38.560 --> 00:40:38.720
Wait.

00:40:38.720 --> 00:40:40.360
[Hello, Sooji]

00:40:40.370 --> 00:40:40.690
Wait, wait.

00:40:40.690 --> 00:40:43.820
[Exhausted]

00:40:43.820 --> 00:40:44.740
Who am I?

00:40:45.040 --> 00:40:46.420
[Oh no...]

00:40:46.610 --> 00:40:47.940
[Everyone knows...]

00:40:48.280 --> 00:40:50.260
[Sooji.]

00:40:50.610 --> 00:40:53.010
[Oh, Merry Christmas.]

00:40:53.430 --> 00:40:55.460
[Happy... Happy New Year.]

00:40:55.860 --> 00:40:57.060
[You're so beautiful.]

00:40:57.740 --> 00:41:00.760
[Thank... you.]

00:41:05.310 --> 00:41:06.660
[Are you Psy?]

00:41:06.880 --> 00:41:08.840
[I'm not Psy. I'm Lee Sooji...]

00:41:09.220 --> 00:41:11.250
[He really can't recognize...]

00:41:11.620 --> 00:41:15.350
[This level of disguise won't work…]

00:41:15.690 --> 00:41:16.790
[First…]

00:41:16.790 --> 00:41:20.710
[-Manager: We still have a Santa suit!
-Forget the disguise.
I'll just wear a hat and sunglasses.]

00:41:20.930 --> 00:41:22.330
[Listening.]
[Manager: We have other props.]

00:41:22.330 --> 00:41:24.290
A Santa suit sounds good.

00:41:24.480 --> 00:41:25.970
[On YouTube: Sooji transforms into Mariah Carey]
[Source: Lee Sooji socials]

00:41:25.970 --> 00:41:27.630
[The Santa suit she used back then.]
[Source: Lee Sooji socials]

00:41:27.630 --> 00:41:27.920
Right. Casual clothes with a beard—

00:41:27.920 --> 00:41:28.990
[Yeah, the problem is the outfit!]

00:41:28.990 --> 00:41:31.010
People will think it's weird, right?

00:41:31.010 --> 00:41:31.140
But if I walk around in a Santa suit,

00:41:31.140 --> 00:41:32.670
[If I walk around in a Santa suit...]

00:41:32.670 --> 00:41:32.880
people will think I'm doing a promo.

00:41:32.880 --> 00:41:35.460
[(Santa suit delivered)]

00:41:35.640 --> 00:41:35.660
[Transforming into Santa!]

00:41:35.660 --> 00:41:36.770
Alright.

00:41:37.020 --> 00:41:38.120
Alright, alright.

00:41:38.650 --> 00:41:39.740
[Who could recognize me like this?]

00:41:39.740 --> 00:41:40.440
Right?

00:41:40.790 --> 00:41:44.280
[Brilliant idea: slick the hair back—
no one knows if it's a man or a woman.]

00:41:44.460 --> 00:41:44.570
-You really look like Psy now. -Really.

00:41:44.570 --> 00:41:46.160
[Oh, you really look like Psy.]

00:41:48.090 --> 00:41:48.210
[Put on sunglasses—complete!]

00:41:48.210 --> 00:41:50.280
I look trendy now.

00:41:50.640 --> 00:41:51.440
It's perfect.

00:41:51.580 --> 00:41:52.050
Guys, you should've given me this earlier.

00:41:52.050 --> 00:41:54.700
[Utterly confident
in her perfect cover-up]

00:41:54.700 --> 00:41:55.950
Okay. Okay.

00:41:56.090 --> 00:41:57.600
[Nobody will recognize me, right?]

00:41:57.600 --> 00:41:58.020
I'm going.

00:41:58.020 --> 00:41:58.520
[Lee Sooji Forever]

00:41:58.520 --> 00:42:00.620
I'm going to deliver it to Jennie.

00:42:06.150 --> 00:42:08.020
[Oh no, I can't find the car...]

00:42:08.300 --> 00:42:08.950
[No riding Rudolf today.
I'm taking a taxi instead.]

00:42:08.950 --> 00:42:10.520
What should I do?

00:42:11.480 --> 00:42:14.210
[Hey, kid, come here.]

00:42:14.940 --> 00:42:16.400
[Did you do good deeds today? No?]

00:42:16.400 --> 00:42:17.790
-No. -No?

00:42:17.790 --> 00:42:18.140
[A kid spotting Santa approaching]

00:42:18.140 --> 00:42:20.580
Okay. Do you want to sit here?

00:42:21.560 --> 00:42:23.620
[-Are you back from school? -Yes.]

00:42:23.620 --> 00:42:24.420
Really?

00:42:24.740 --> 00:42:27.760
[Tell me what good deeds
you did this year.]

00:42:28.020 --> 00:42:31.360
[Uh… I listened to Mom…]

00:42:31.530 --> 00:42:33.070
[Only a part…]

00:42:33.070 --> 00:42:33.280
So you only listened to part of what Mom said?

00:42:33.280 --> 00:42:35.340
[An honest kid]

00:42:35.340 --> 00:42:35.600
Hold on.

00:42:35.600 --> 00:42:36.810
[Rummaging]

00:42:36.810 --> 00:42:38.150
Grandpa here...

00:42:38.400 --> 00:42:40.820
[I've got a gift for you.]

00:42:41.610 --> 00:42:42.980
[This...]

00:42:44.360 --> 00:42:45.940
[-How about using it as a bookmark?
-What? ]

00:42:45.940 --> 00:42:47.690
-What? -A bookmark.

00:42:47.690 --> 00:42:49.170
[What's a bookmark?]

00:42:49.170 --> 00:42:50.590
It's something you put in a book to mark the page.

00:42:50.590 --> 00:42:54.270
[Unfortunately, it's an unwanted supply…]

00:42:55.310 --> 00:42:57.070
[You don't like it?]

00:42:57.370 --> 00:42:59.110
[What do you want then?]

00:42:59.210 --> 00:42:59.410
What do you want then?

00:42:59.410 --> 00:43:01.270
[Startled by the sudden real voice]

00:43:01.540 --> 00:43:02.010
[Oh my...]

00:43:02.010 --> 00:43:02.870
You...

00:43:03.190 --> 00:43:06.010
[What... hahaha... do you want?]

00:43:08.450 --> 00:43:10.550
[Lively.][Sorry, I don't have
anything for you…]

00:43:10.550 --> 00:43:12.380
[Big-hearted][Not a single thing, really…]

00:43:13.170 --> 00:43:13.410
-Where are you going? -What?

00:43:13.410 --> 00:43:15.570
[Where are you going?]

00:43:15.780 --> 00:43:18.670
[I... Where...]

00:43:18.870 --> 00:43:20.420
[I'm... not going anywhere.]

00:43:20.600 --> 00:43:22.850
[Why are you here, kid?]

00:43:23.020 --> 00:43:25.660
[Because... inside...]

00:43:25.850 --> 00:43:29.150
[-My family is inside. -Ah, restaurant?]

00:43:29.450 --> 00:43:30.990
[-Eating? -No?]

00:43:30.990 --> 00:43:32.770
-No. -What are they doing?

00:43:33.080 --> 00:43:34.400
[-Is the restaurant your home? -No? ]

00:43:34.400 --> 00:43:36.050
-No. -Then what?

00:43:36.240 --> 00:43:37.150
[It's a shop!]

00:43:37.150 --> 00:43:37.510
-So it's your family's shop? -Yes.

00:43:37.510 --> 00:43:39.570
[Curiosity-baiting conversation]

00:43:39.830 --> 00:43:41.420
[Hey, you punk!]

00:43:41.650 --> 00:43:43.580
[What, you gonna inherit the business?]

00:43:43.870 --> 00:43:45.040
[Isn't this place a gourmet restaurant?]

00:43:45.040 --> 00:43:46.550
[This place is packed!]

00:43:46.820 --> 00:43:49.110
[-Then it'll be your shop, right? -Yes!]

00:43:49.110 --> 00:43:50.590
-Yes. -You're so lucky!

00:43:50.590 --> 00:43:50.760
[A kid born with gifts!]

00:43:50.760 --> 00:43:52.330
That place is also my family’s shop.

00:43:52.330 --> 00:43:54.540
Whoa, kid.

00:43:54.680 --> 00:43:57.310
[Dad works here, Grandpa works there.]

00:43:57.550 --> 00:44:00.680
[What? Then you give me something!]

00:44:00.680 --> 00:44:00.940
Didn't I already give you this?

00:44:00.940 --> 00:44:02.340
[Santa turning the tables]

00:44:02.610 --> 00:44:03.020
[Searching]

00:44:03.020 --> 00:44:03.740
-I don't have any. -You didn't?

00:44:03.740 --> 00:44:04.920
[I don't have any?]

00:44:05.150 --> 00:44:05.600
[Innocence: A precious gift.]

00:44:05.600 --> 00:44:07.350
-No. -No? How cute.

00:44:07.790 --> 00:44:07.930
[Bow]

00:44:07.930 --> 00:44:09.540
See you next time.

00:44:09.640 --> 00:44:10.940
[Thank you.]

00:44:11.080 --> 00:44:13.340
Because he only listened a little to Mom,

00:44:13.420 --> 00:44:15.460
no gift for him this year.

00:44:15.460 --> 00:44:18.670
[Do you want to join
the Manito Club, too?]

00:44:19.450 --> 00:44:19.490
[Meanwhile, Jennie goes to find Dex.]

00:44:19.490 --> 00:44:21.490
What should we do?

00:44:22.790 --> 00:44:26.040
[Jennie: We have to get there
before he finishes the pork cutlet.]

00:44:26.230 --> 00:44:26.500
I'll check the area as I pass by.

00:44:26.500 --> 00:44:29.290
[Jennie's plan 1: Scout the location
while passing.]

00:44:29.290 --> 00:44:30.380
We're almost there.

00:44:30.380 --> 00:44:31.160
[About five minutes away.]

00:44:31.160 --> 00:44:33.140
We'll get there in five minutes.

00:44:34.380 --> 00:44:38.770
[Dex: For the first gift,
I'll take the risk.]

00:44:38.930 --> 00:44:40.670
[Ring and run.]

00:44:40.670 --> 00:44:41.800
It's been a while...

00:44:41.920 --> 00:44:43.500
[Put the gift down. Knock.]

00:44:44.240 --> 00:44:44.300
Knock at the door. I have to try.

00:44:44.300 --> 00:44:46.290
[Former agent team's ring-and-run skill.]

00:44:47.160 --> 00:44:47.970
Guys, we're about to pass his spot.

00:44:47.970 --> 00:44:50.740
[JEN Team Captain ready to ambush.]

00:44:50.740 --> 00:44:53.780
Let's leave this alley.

00:44:53.840 --> 00:44:55.740
[Dex's location]
[Jennie: Hide when I tell you.]

00:44:55.740 --> 00:44:56.140
Got it?

00:44:56.280 --> 00:44:58.080
[Dex's location]
[Jennie: We will pass by from a distance.]

00:44:58.370 --> 00:45:00.670
[Dex: Actually, all we need to do
is just head out, right?]

00:45:00.790 --> 00:45:01.010
Anywhere, immediately.

00:45:01.010 --> 00:45:03.360
[Confident]

00:45:03.550 --> 00:45:06.210
[[Jennie's car] [Dex]

00:45:06.210 --> 00:45:08.370
[[Jennie's car] [Dex]
[Go to the next alley to park as planned.]

00:45:08.370 --> 00:45:09.490
Okay.

00:45:09.650 --> 00:45:10.890
Be careful. Watch the camera.

00:45:10.890 --> 00:45:12.230
[Watch the camera!][Dex's location]

00:45:12.400 --> 00:45:13.580
This won't work.

00:45:13.710 --> 00:45:15.140
[Oh my god,
this is an apartment complex…!]

00:45:15.140 --> 00:45:16.670
What should we do?

00:45:16.870 --> 00:45:17.010
Gosh, I'm sorry.
Will you lift the gate for me?

00:45:17.010 --> 00:45:20.890
[Accidentally entering the complex]

00:45:21.620 --> 00:45:23.580
[I'll circle out…]

00:45:23.810 --> 00:45:26.710
[I'll leave… sir…]

00:45:27.660 --> 00:45:29.650
[Sorry, I'll turn around~]

00:45:30.060 --> 00:45:30.070
[Jennie's plan is a bit rough.]

00:45:30.070 --> 00:45:31.320
Well...

00:45:31.520 --> 00:45:33.590
There's no parking place, and...

00:45:34.490 --> 00:45:38.220
[(Secretly) Jennie: We have to
be very careful now.]

00:45:38.540 --> 00:45:41.670
[Dex's location][What should we do?]

00:45:41.670 --> 00:45:42.230
[Dex's location]

00:45:42.230 --> 00:45:43.690
What should I do?

00:45:44.700 --> 00:45:45.010
This is insane. For real.

00:45:45.010 --> 00:45:46.380
[This is insane. This is insane.]

00:45:46.920 --> 00:45:48.380
[Jennie: But If we keep stalling up front,]

00:45:48.380 --> 00:45:50.490
[Jennie: I might get caught.]

00:45:50.790 --> 00:45:52.590
[Jennie parking right under his nose.]

00:45:52.590 --> 00:45:54.150
Wait.

00:45:54.290 --> 00:45:56.400
That is hard.

00:45:56.440 --> 00:45:59.140
[It's not easy to be a Manito.]

00:45:59.490 --> 00:46:01.710
[Feels like I'm an agent.]

00:46:04.680 --> 00:46:06.920
[Let's go.]

00:46:07.430 --> 00:46:09.280
[This feels too risky.]

00:46:09.660 --> 00:46:09.820
I'm standing up.

00:46:09.820 --> 00:46:12.000
[At the same time, Dex
stands up from the seat.]

00:46:12.070 --> 00:46:12.340
I'm full, thanks to you guys.

00:46:12.340 --> 00:46:14.590
[I'm full.]

00:46:14.980 --> 00:46:17.520
[Nervous]

00:46:17.920 --> 00:46:20.330
[The distance closes again.]

00:46:20.330 --> 00:46:21.770
Be careful. Watch the camera.

00:46:21.770 --> 00:46:23.620
[Jennie's car]
[Trying to enter the restaurant]

00:46:23.960 --> 00:46:26.760
[Careful.]

00:46:27.500 --> 00:46:29.790
[Check, please.]

00:46:30.400 --> 00:46:33.100
[Careful.]

00:46:33.430 --> 00:46:35.770
[At this rate, she might get caught!]

00:46:37.360 --> 00:46:38.770
Oh, no. What should we do? Wait.

00:46:38.770 --> 00:46:38.930
Oh, no. What should we do? Wait.

00:46:38.930 --> 00:46:39.930
[The restaurant door suddenly opens]

00:46:39.930 --> 00:46:41.030
Wait a minute.

00:46:41.150 --> 00:46:41.870
No. Let's go.

00:46:41.870 --> 00:46:42.960
[Panic]

00:46:42.960 --> 00:46:44.000
Let's go

00:46:44.100 --> 00:46:44.380
Let's go.

00:46:44.380 --> 00:46:48.920
[Strategic? right turn again]

00:46:50.150 --> 00:46:52.010
[Thanks, I'm done eating.]

00:46:53.930 --> 00:46:56.490
[By seconds—Dex appears]

00:46:56.490 --> 00:46:58.330
-He's behind me. -I'm done.

00:46:58.440 --> 00:46:59.570
I'm done.

00:46:59.960 --> 00:47:00.040
[Where are you going?]

00:47:00.040 --> 00:47:01.550
Where are you going?

00:47:01.750 --> 00:47:03.020
Where are you going?

00:47:03.020 --> 00:47:06.260
[Dex is moving!]

00:47:08.300 --> 00:47:10.880
[Is he coming this way?]

00:47:11.180 --> 00:47:11.250
The car key.

00:47:11.250 --> 00:47:13.800
[An irrepressible racing instinct]

00:47:13.800 --> 00:47:14.570
I gotta go. I gotta go.

00:47:14.570 --> 00:47:18.660
[Sprinting back to the gym.]

00:47:19.730 --> 00:47:22.240
[How many laps
have I driven around here already...]

00:47:22.330 --> 00:47:22.490
I won't be able to deliver the gift.

00:47:22.490 --> 00:47:25.090
[At this rate, I won't be able
to deliver the gift....?]

00:47:25.510 --> 00:47:30.080
[Who told you
to wear a sweater to work today...]

00:47:30.080 --> 00:47:30.570
I'm almost there.

00:47:30.570 --> 00:47:31.300
[Where did Dex go after the meal?]

00:47:31.300 --> 00:47:32.720
Right here.

00:47:32.730 --> 00:47:33.110
What is he doing in the gym?

00:47:33.110 --> 00:47:35.350
[What is he doing?]

00:47:36.020 --> 00:47:36.040
[Car key...]

00:47:36.040 --> 00:47:38.120
My car key.

00:47:39.710 --> 00:47:40.200
Where is he?

00:47:40.200 --> 00:47:41.310
[Jennie closing in on Dex's location
for the 5th time]

00:47:41.310 --> 00:47:43.120
Can this work?

00:47:43.220 --> 00:47:44.020
Wait.

00:47:44.120 --> 00:47:44.670
Where is he? What if he's looking at me?

00:47:44.670 --> 00:47:46.920
[Anxious]

00:47:47.260 --> 00:47:50.270
[Jennie: Where is he? The cafe?]

00:47:50.330 --> 00:47:50.730
This way.

00:47:50.730 --> 00:47:53.280
[Meanwhile, Dex gets the car]

00:47:55.650 --> 00:48:00.310
[DEX Black Box CAM:
Entrance obstructed. Pulling over.]

00:48:02.890 --> 00:48:04.790
[Hide]

00:48:08.170 --> 00:48:11.500
[A quick peek. Closing in on Dex,
50 meters ahead, to deliver the first gift!]

00:48:17.240 --> 00:48:18.790
Where is he?

00:48:21.390 --> 00:48:23.320
[An obvious basement gym]

00:48:24.030 --> 00:48:26.700
[Jennie: How do I get to B1?]

00:48:30.980 --> 00:48:33.440
[Found the entrance!]

00:48:33.440 --> 00:48:34.000
I gotta go. I gotta go.

00:48:34.000 --> 00:48:35.800
[The place where Dex ran 3 minutes ago]

00:48:38.820 --> 00:48:39.260
Okay.

00:48:39.260 --> 00:48:40.990
[Pull]

00:48:47.840 --> 00:48:49.900
[Dex: I'm operating in secret today,]

00:48:49.900 --> 00:48:51.280
so I'm wearing a hat.

00:48:51.400 --> 00:48:51.740
I hope you can understand.

00:48:51.740 --> 00:48:57.080
[Dex black box CAM: Jennie
is walking past Dex.]

00:48:57.220 --> 00:48:58.920
I'll cover the tag.

00:49:04.190 --> 00:49:05.060
Is there a gym downstairs?

00:49:05.060 --> 00:49:09.180
[Jennie: Is there a gym downstairs?]

00:49:09.180 --> 00:49:09.690
-It's for Chu Sunghoon. -Is there a gym downstairs?

00:49:09.690 --> 00:49:11.270
[He doesn't know Jennie is here.
He's preparing Sunghoon's gift.]

00:49:11.270 --> 00:49:13.330
The first gift is ready.

00:49:13.670 --> 00:49:13.750
[Dex black box CAM: Heart-stopping moment.]

00:49:13.750 --> 00:49:15.730
I'll write a note.

00:49:16.690 --> 00:49:18.870
My first note.

00:49:20.460 --> 00:49:21.260
[Brave]

00:49:26.700 --> 00:49:28.180
[Please follow me.]

00:49:28.880 --> 00:49:31.190
[I'm 100% sure it's here!]

00:49:31.190 --> 00:49:32.160
He's working out.

00:49:32.160 --> 00:49:32.290
[Targeted vitamins for post-workout!]

00:49:32.290 --> 00:49:34.620
It's a perfect time for some vitamins.

00:49:36.320 --> 00:49:39.250
[I don't know what will happen
when I open the door]

00:49:41.410 --> 00:49:45.040
[Nervous]

00:49:52.250 --> 00:49:54.350
[I think he's there!!!!]

00:49:54.350 --> 00:49:55.700
Wait.

00:49:58.430 --> 00:50:02.340
[Tiptoeing]

00:50:02.530 --> 00:50:03.940
[Jennie: Director, help me.]

00:50:03.940 --> 00:50:05.670
Hold this for me.

