01:09:01.080 --> 01:09:02.359
Just said I finished my mission.

01:09:02.359 --> 01:09:04.170
I am doing it to get the first benefit.

01:09:04.170 --> 01:09:04.370
I will give you a gift, Jennie.

01:09:04.370 --> 01:09:06.840
[Sooji: Let's get the benefits
and go for a bigger gift!]

01:09:06.840 --> 01:09:07.300
Almost there. Almost there.

01:09:07.300 --> 01:09:08.340
[The two are running for the first gift]

01:09:08.340 --> 01:09:09.979
Let's go upstairs first.

01:09:10.529 --> 01:09:11.910
Almost there.

01:09:12.350 --> 01:09:14.830
[Jennie is within 400 meters!]

01:09:14.990 --> 01:09:15.240
Run.

01:09:15.240 --> 01:09:18.319
[2:14PM: 400 meters
in front of Jennie's company]

01:09:18.800 --> 01:09:22.100
[The rush to deliver the gift
in every second]

01:09:24.660 --> 01:09:26.060
[Lee Sooji: We're getting closer!]

01:09:29.130 --> 01:09:31.319
[Santa is running in the center of Seoul]

01:09:32.290 --> 01:09:33.370
[Braking in a hurry]

01:09:33.960 --> 01:09:37.300
[The uphill road of hell]

01:09:42.279 --> 01:09:44.609
[The footsteps that suddenly slowed down]

01:09:45.029 --> 01:09:45.590
[Ho...]

01:09:46.170 --> 01:09:47.149
[Ho]

01:09:47.990 --> 01:09:51.319
[You go on, I'm too tired to keep going.]

01:09:51.740 --> 01:09:54.980
[A long, difficult way to send gifts]

01:09:56.280 --> 01:09:58.220
[Lee Sooji: Don't you taste blood?!]

01:09:58.440 --> 01:09:59.740
[Hahahaha...]

01:10:00.490 --> 01:10:01.240
[Hahaha...]

01:10:02.140 --> 01:10:04.660
[Hey...]

01:10:05.370 --> 01:10:06.970
[Lee Sooji: Let's walk slowly...]

01:10:07.080 --> 01:10:07.180
Shoot me from around the corner.

01:10:07.180 --> 01:10:10.890
[2:20PM: Entering the lobby of Hotel
where Sunghoon stays]

01:10:11.590 --> 01:10:14.200
[Carefully]

01:10:16.370 --> 01:10:20.270
[Dex: Can we go upstairs?]

01:10:20.600 --> 01:10:23.270
[Dex: That should be the lobby.]

01:10:23.780 --> 01:10:28.700
[Dex: Hello I'm Dex...]

01:10:28.700 --> 01:10:30.780
[Dex: I’m really sorry.
We're shooting right now...]

01:10:30.780 --> 01:10:33.010
[Dex: We have something to deliver.]

01:10:33.010 --> 01:10:36.240
[Dex: Can you come up with me?]

01:10:36.710 --> 01:10:36.720
[Staff: I'll go up with you.]

01:10:36.720 --> 01:10:38.850
-I'll go with you.
-Okay.

01:10:39.290 --> 01:10:40.430
Thank you.

01:10:40.940 --> 01:10:42.410
[Dex]

01:10:42.410 --> 01:10:44.580
[Dex]
[Employee: Do you want to
put it in our shopping bag?]

01:10:44.580 --> 01:10:46.870
[Dex: That would be great. Thank you~]

01:10:47.370 --> 01:10:49.980
[Dex]
[Using the hotel shopping bag
for a more perfect disguise]

01:10:50.300 --> 01:10:52.400
[2:25PM: 80m in front of Jennie's company]

01:10:53.260 --> 01:10:54.440
[Lee Sooji: Almost there. Almost there.]

01:10:54.440 --> 01:10:55.480
[Almost there.]

01:10:56.230 --> 01:10:58.800
[Lee Sooji: Ah, I see. In the office?]

01:10:59.170 --> 01:11:00.400
[Haha!]

01:11:00.960 --> 01:11:02.260
[Poking]

01:11:02.460 --> 01:11:03.940
These names...

01:11:04.220 --> 01:11:04.800
These names...

01:11:04.800 --> 01:11:06.960
[Still vigilant]

01:11:07.960 --> 01:11:09.780
[Jennie: No.]

01:11:09.780 --> 01:11:11.520
[Are you watching~?]

01:11:12.790 --> 01:11:12.830
I don't think anyone will recognize me.

01:11:12.830 --> 01:11:14.510
[Believing in Santa Macaulay's outfit
and marches forward with confidence]

01:11:14.510 --> 01:11:16.580
I don't think anyone would recognize me.

01:11:16.580 --> 01:11:17.980
[Take a look]

01:11:18.240 --> 01:11:21.010
[Enter the building without hesitation]

01:11:22.420 --> 01:11:23.760
[Bow]

01:11:26.280 --> 01:11:29.790
[Macaulay goes downstairs boldly]

01:11:30.480 --> 01:11:34.330
[Where is Jennie~?]

01:11:38.380 --> 01:11:40.910
[Don’t know how to get in, feeling lost]

01:11:44.450 --> 01:11:46.670
[Hello, excuse me...]
[Spotted someone entering the building]

01:11:47.000 --> 01:11:50.250
[Are you going to the office?
Lee Sooji: Do you know which floor
Jennie's office is on?]

01:11:50.250 --> 01:11:51.810
-To the office?
-Yes.

01:11:52.130 --> 01:11:54.470
[What?
Lee Sooji: Can I come in too?]

01:11:55.250 --> 01:11:56.540
[Jennie~]

01:11:56.810 --> 01:11:59.440
[With too much trust in Macaulay's outfit,
she boldly walked in
while shouting her name]

01:11:59.700 --> 01:12:02.550
[Turn around]

01:12:02.790 --> 01:12:03.220
Okay. Thank you.

01:12:03.220 --> 01:12:05.510
[2:26 PM: Dex takes the elevator
with the help of the staff]

01:12:05.510 --> 01:12:07.160
Okay? Okay.

01:12:08.870 --> 01:12:12.400
[Filming was done
with the hotel's assistance]

01:12:12.740 --> 01:12:14.690
[Dex: Since this is a surprise gift,]

01:12:14.690 --> 01:12:18.370
[Dex: that’s why it’s like this.
Please don't misunderstand.]

01:12:18.370 --> 01:12:19.360
[Employee:
I'll accompany you to this floor.]

01:12:19.360 --> 01:12:21.560
Thank you. You really know your job.

01:12:21.800 --> 01:12:23.680
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

01:12:23.940 --> 01:12:25.940
[Successfully sneak in]

01:12:28.520 --> 01:12:31.600
[Carefully]

01:12:33.210 --> 01:12:34.790
[Choo Sunghoon: I think it's okay(?)]

01:12:34.840 --> 01:12:35.110
Okay.

01:12:35.110 --> 01:12:38.270
[Take a big step]

01:12:39.010 --> 01:12:44.840
[Dex: Wait Let's take a look
at the corridor first...]

01:12:45.530 --> 01:12:49.690
[Using the phone as a mirrow]

01:12:50.360 --> 01:12:54.190
[Poking]

01:12:56.770 --> 01:13:00.780
[Carefully confirming the
distance to the destination]

01:13:01.110 --> 01:13:02.680
[Dex: Just stay here.]

01:13:02.680 --> 01:13:03.760
[Dex: I'll be back soon.]

01:13:05.670 --> 01:13:07.810
[Dex: I'm going.]

01:13:19.350 --> 01:13:21.170
Yes. Yes.

01:13:21.690 --> 01:13:24.140
[Shall we go now?]

01:13:30.310 --> 01:13:31.760
Okay.

01:13:32.700 --> 01:13:33.850
[Choo Sunghoon: Well...]

01:13:38.640 --> 01:13:40.440
[The crew: Did you get the address
of the motorcycle shop?]

01:13:40.440 --> 01:13:41.800
[Choo Sunghoon: Yes, I got it.]

01:14:04.940 --> 01:14:06.140
[Oh what?]

01:14:11.140 --> 01:14:11.360
[In a thrilling instant,
the door opened in just 3 seconds]

01:14:11.360 --> 01:14:12.470
What?

01:14:19.900 --> 01:14:24.890
[Is giving a gift
supposed to be this stressful...]

01:14:25.810 --> 01:14:27.200
[Panicking
Let's go upstairs, upstairs.]

01:14:27.200 --> 01:14:28.090
Can we go upstairs?

01:14:28.090 --> 01:14:30.020
I don't know. Where should I press?

01:14:32.980 --> 01:14:34.470
[P-Protein powder?]

01:14:34.710 --> 01:14:36.790
[Does the hotel
even give out protein powder?]

01:14:37.820 --> 01:14:40.580
[Gasping...]

01:14:41.110 --> 01:14:43.310
[Dex: I was too impatient...]

01:14:43.580 --> 01:14:47.330
[Dex: I ran as soon as
I rang the doorbell.]

01:14:49.670 --> 01:14:49.810
[2:32 PM
Dex sends out the gift]

01:14:49.810 --> 01:14:51.670
Why isn't there any reaction yet?

01:14:51.690 --> 01:14:52.770
Why didn't I get a notification?

01:14:52.770 --> 01:14:55.020
[Still hasn't received the first
gift confirmation, feeling anxious]

01:14:55.390 --> 01:14:56.510
[The crew:
She's in another building…]

01:14:56.510 --> 01:14:57.120
[3 minutes ago – Macaulay Team]

01:14:57.120 --> 01:14:57.640
What? I'm doomed.

01:14:57.640 --> 01:14:59.300
[I'm doomed QAQ;
3 minutes ago, Macaulay Team]

01:14:59.900 --> 01:15:02.290
[2:29 PM The lost Santa, Macaulay]

01:15:03.470 --> 01:15:05.320
[Looking left and right]

01:15:06.340 --> 01:15:07.710
[Ah—this is the place!]

01:15:08.040 --> 01:15:08.050
It's here. Found it.

01:15:08.050 --> 01:15:11.320
[Spotted Jennie’s company
right next door.]

01:15:11.720 --> 01:15:15.240
[Good thing it's the building next door.]

01:15:15.490 --> 01:15:15.630
No one will recognize me, right?

01:15:15.630 --> 01:15:17.450
[I, Macaulay, am completely
serious about this disguise]

01:15:17.450 --> 01:15:19.010
No one will recognize me, right?

01:15:19.010 --> 01:15:19.300
Is this really one out of ten boxes?

01:15:19.300 --> 01:15:22.270
[Jennie peacefully opening cookies]

01:15:22.770 --> 01:15:22.850
What should I do…

01:15:22.850 --> 01:15:24.320
[Whoosh—]

01:15:24.570 --> 01:15:27.220
[A red silhouette casually passing by]

01:15:30.690 --> 01:15:33.290
[The first gift is delivered by me!]

01:15:37.090 --> 01:15:40.530
[Unhesitating footsteps]

01:15:43.470 --> 01:15:44.310
[Beep]

01:15:45.110 --> 01:15:47.360
[Opens the access door]

01:15:47.830 --> 01:15:49.930
[Pokes head in]

01:15:50.310 --> 01:15:51.600
I think that's how I should do it.

01:15:51.600 --> 01:15:53.250
[Turns around]

01:15:57.800 --> 01:16:00.540
[That's so bold…?]

01:16:03.840 --> 01:16:06.240
[It's Santa Claus!]

01:16:06.900 --> 01:16:10.290
[Panics the moment she sees Jennie]

01:16:10.600 --> 01:16:12.100
[Runs away first]

01:16:12.390 --> 01:16:14.230
[Fidgeting]

01:16:17.380 --> 01:16:18.460
[What is this?]

01:16:18.700 --> 01:16:19.940
Who are you?

01:16:19.940 --> 01:16:20.180
[Drops it immediately]

01:16:20.180 --> 01:16:21.610
Who are you?

01:16:21.740 --> 01:16:21.900
Who are you?

01:16:21.900 --> 01:16:22.990
[2:?? PM
In a panic,]

01:16:22.990 --> 01:16:23.320
Who are you?

01:16:23.320 --> 01:16:25.290
[2:?? PM
she put it on the ground and fled.]

01:16:25.680 --> 01:16:28.460
[Save Santa Claus]

01:16:28.790 --> 01:16:30.020
[What was that…?]

01:16:32.750 --> 01:16:35.200
[Full-speed sprint]

01:16:35.520 --> 01:16:37.200
[All alone…]

01:16:37.580 --> 01:16:38.810
[Uh… Santa Claus…]

01:16:38.810 --> 01:16:40.690
[Oh! Is my Manito the Raccoon Dog?!]

01:16:41.650 --> 01:16:42.680
[Camera director: (Me too) I can smell blood…!]

01:16:42.680 --> 01:16:45.140
[Earnest—may I hitch a ride in your car?]

01:16:46.520 --> 01:16:47.860
[What is this~?]

01:16:47.860 --> 01:16:49.100
[What is this~~?]

01:16:49.510 --> 01:16:51.340
[Picks up the gift]

01:16:51.610 --> 01:16:54.490
[I received a gift~~~]

01:16:54.790 --> 01:16:55.410
[So special…!]

01:16:55.410 --> 01:16:59.010
[They must be exhausted
running uphill like that, right?!]

01:16:59.260 --> 01:17:02.670
[Ha… correct answer.]

01:17:03.900 --> 01:17:05.780
[When I opened the door and went inside…]

01:17:06.020 --> 01:17:07.760
[I thought it would be a parking lot.]

01:17:07.760 --> 01:17:09.590
[But Jennie was sitting right there.]

01:17:09.750 --> 01:17:11.490
[Jennie saw me!]

01:17:11.560 --> 01:17:11.920
Jennie… I thought
I had to give her the doll.

01:17:11.920 --> 01:17:13.400
[So exhausted that she suddenly slips into
Lee Jung-jae’s tone from The Face Reader]

01:17:13.400 --> 01:17:14.880
[(Source: Lee Jung-jae's socials)]

01:17:15.110 --> 01:17:16.790
[I opened the door again]

01:17:16.990 --> 01:17:18.650
[After placing it down, Jennie said]

01:17:18.650 --> 01:17:20.260
["Who are you?"]

01:17:20.260 --> 01:17:22.100
["Who are you?"]

01:17:22.580 --> 01:17:22.600
We did it.

01:17:22.600 --> 01:17:24.710
[Exploding dopamine from gift delivery]

01:17:24.710 --> 01:17:26.240
It was actually pretty fun.

01:17:26.880 --> 01:17:28.180
[Ah~ She probably doesn't know, right?]

01:17:28.180 --> 01:17:29.970
[Completely unnoticed!]

01:17:30.350 --> 01:17:32.260
[But somehow…]

01:17:32.260 --> 01:17:34.610
[That silhouette…!]

01:17:34.850 --> 01:17:36.720
[Who was that…?]

01:17:37.010 --> 01:17:38.830
[That was way too obvious, wasn't it…?]

01:17:38.830 --> 01:17:41.030
[But! I didn't see the face.]

01:17:41.270 --> 01:17:42.210
[I have to do it that way~]

01:17:42.210 --> 01:17:43.110
[A disguise…!]

01:17:43.110 --> 01:17:46.020
[I need to disguise myself…!!!!]

01:17:47.300 --> 01:17:48.780
[Ow]

01:17:49.090 --> 01:17:51.710
[Huh? Sunghoon is also checking his gift]

01:17:52.380 --> 01:17:58.820
[Pick... like...]

01:17:59.140 --> 01:18:00.780
[They want me to pick
what I like?]

01:18:03.540 --> 01:18:05.350
[This one!]

01:18:05.350 --> 01:18:05.670
The highest protein content.

01:18:05.670 --> 01:18:06.830
[Chose the one
with the highest protein content]

01:18:06.830 --> 01:18:08.230
This one's only 40 grams.

01:18:08.580 --> 01:18:10.200
[This one's just over 20 grams.]

01:18:10.350 --> 01:18:10.420
This one's double. I'll take this.

01:18:10.420 --> 01:18:12.690
[Chose purely based on protein content]

01:18:14.290 --> 01:18:14.450
Thanks.

01:18:14.450 --> 01:18:15.890
[Masculine man expressing gratitude]

01:18:15.890 --> 01:18:17.730
Alright, let's head out then.

01:18:17.950 --> 01:18:21.070
[Three hours into Manito,
he finally went out to buy the gift.]

01:18:21.410 --> 01:18:23.760
[Dex: Sorry,
I just went to deliver something.]

01:18:23.760 --> 01:18:25.050
[Dex: Can you call
and check if it was received?]

01:18:25.050 --> 01:18:27.020
-If it was received.
-Okay.

01:18:27.020 --> 01:18:30.750
[Confirmed with the front desk
whether the gift was delivered]

01:18:30.750 --> 01:18:32.820
Hello, this is the front desk.

01:18:35.180 --> 01:18:36.900
[Ah, he didn't answer the phone?]

01:18:36.900 --> 01:18:37.110
[The staff: We called the guest room,
but there was no answer.]

01:18:37.110 --> 01:18:38.860
-He didn't pick up?
-Yes.

01:18:38.980 --> 01:18:40.230
[Emm…]

01:18:40.450 --> 01:18:42.510
Why wouldn't he answer the phone…?

01:18:42.730 --> 01:18:42.850
Let's go, let's go.

01:18:42.850 --> 01:18:45.680
[At that moment, Sunghoon]

01:18:46.590 --> 01:18:49.400
[Missed the call by just a split second]

01:18:49.700 --> 01:18:52.390
[Dex: But the gift
has to be received in person.]

01:18:52.390 --> 01:18:53.740
[Dex: And he didn't answer the call.]

01:18:53.740 --> 01:18:54.270
What could he be doing?

01:18:54.270 --> 01:18:54.920
[Growing anxious]

01:18:54.920 --> 01:18:56.320
Is he showering?

01:18:56.460 --> 01:18:58.150
It's already 12:30—what's he doing?

01:18:58.150 --> 01:18:59.830
[Wait a second.]

01:19:00.180 --> 01:19:04.390
[At that moment,
a message arrived from the HQ.]

01:19:05.220 --> 01:19:06.500
[It's okay now.]

01:19:06.730 --> 01:19:08.160
[It should have been delivered.]

01:19:08.670 --> 01:19:08.730
Thank you.

01:19:08.730 --> 01:19:10.310
[Politely]

01:19:12.150 --> 01:19:14.570
[Sunghoon walks out into the lobby]

01:19:14.960 --> 01:19:15.570
[Casually retreating from behind]

01:19:15.570 --> 01:19:17.630
Looks like the taxi's here, isn't it?

01:19:18.780 --> 01:19:19.700
[Success. Success!!!]

01:19:19.700 --> 01:19:21.010
[The crew:
He's right behind us…!!!]

01:19:21.380 --> 01:19:22.100
[What is it? What is it?]

01:19:22.100 --> 01:19:23.700
[Is he behind us?]

01:19:24.000 --> 01:19:25.590
[What's going on? What's going on?
What's going on?]

01:19:25.590 --> 01:19:27.690
[Did he see me?
The crew: Choo Sunghoon is behind us!]

01:19:27.690 --> 01:19:29.720
[The crew: He didn't see us.
He can see us if we're here.]

01:19:30.120 --> 01:19:34.510
[Panicking and running away]

01:19:34.800 --> 01:19:36.430
[Did he see me?!]

01:19:36.810 --> 01:19:37.930
[The crew:
He didn't see you at all.]

01:19:37.930 --> 01:19:39.690
[Surprised. I didn't see him either!]

01:19:40.700 --> 01:19:43.750
[Wait—then…
Is Sunghoon hyung in the lobby?]

01:19:44.010 --> 01:19:46.010
[The crew: We took a photo…]

01:19:46.030 --> 01:19:46.230
This is you.

01:19:46.230 --> 01:19:47.710
[Sunghoon → Dex]

01:19:47.710 --> 01:19:49.060
He's right on the left.

01:19:50.510 --> 01:19:52.390
[Sunghoon;
Dex: So I ran off behind his back, right?]

01:19:52.660 --> 01:19:53.380
It's fine. It should be delivered.

01:19:53.380 --> 01:19:55.380
[They almost ran into each other]

01:19:55.380 --> 01:19:56.170
Thank you.

01:20:01.920 --> 01:20:03.680
[Dex: Well, I had no idea at all.
I was acting super casual.]

01:20:03.680 --> 01:20:04.500
[Casual mode]

01:20:04.500 --> 01:20:05.830
I walked past like this.

01:20:05.890 --> 01:20:07.620
I really walked past like this.

01:20:08.060 --> 01:20:09.100
[Hurry, get in the car!]

01:20:09.100 --> 01:20:10.320
[Get in! Get in! Get in! Get in!]

01:20:10.610 --> 01:20:11.770
[Casualness itself]

01:20:11.770 --> 01:20:12.970
Get in! Get in! Get in!

01:20:12.970 --> 01:20:13.990
[Get in! Get in~!]

01:20:13.990 --> 01:20:15.900
[Get in~!]

01:20:16.990 --> 01:20:18.350
[Panicking. Where are the keys? The keys!]

01:20:18.940 --> 01:20:20.720
[Get in… get in…]

01:20:21.180 --> 01:20:25.790
[Sunghoon calmly sits into the taxi]

01:20:29.280 --> 01:20:32.780
[Sweating issue — removes disguise]

01:20:33.780 --> 01:20:35.130
I got the message.

01:20:35.130 --> 01:20:36.770
[Received message from the HQ]

01:20:36.770 --> 01:20:38.300
I got the message.

01:20:38.680 --> 01:20:39.870
[Huh? "The first gift
of Manito Club has been delivered."]

01:20:39.870 --> 01:20:40.990
The first gift.

01:20:41.100 --> 01:20:43.910
The first gift has been delivered.

01:20:45.570 --> 01:20:47.500
The first gift has been delivered.

01:20:47.680 --> 01:20:49.020
[Wasn't that just now?]

01:20:49.440 --> 01:20:50.600
[Pro… protein powder?]

01:20:50.600 --> 01:20:50.780
[The protein powder Sunghoon received?]

01:20:50.780 --> 01:20:52.020
It's protein powder.

01:20:52.840 --> 01:20:55.720
[Was I the one
who received the first gift?!]

01:20:55.720 --> 01:20:56.020
Travel together with adorable Rudolph!

01:20:56.020 --> 01:20:57.680
[The Rudolph that Jennie received?]

01:20:57.680 --> 01:20:59.190
Wishing you lots of luck.

01:20:59.290 --> 01:20:59.370
The first gift has been delivered.

01:20:59.370 --> 01:21:00.520
[The one who delivered the gift first is?]

01:21:00.520 --> 01:21:02.780
The Manito who delivered the gift first.

01:21:03.540 --> 01:21:05.140
[Oh? By a tiny margin!]

01:21:05.330 --> 01:21:06.010
[Two minutes…!]

01:21:06.210 --> 01:21:07.640
[Only a 2-minute difference!]

01:21:07.880 --> 01:21:08.100
[So intense]

01:21:08.100 --> 01:21:09.630
Just two minutes.

01:21:09.770 --> 01:21:14.080
[Dex decisively delivering the gift —
rings the doorbell and runs away.]

01:21:14.460 --> 01:21:14.670
[PM 2:32]

01:21:14.670 --> 01:21:15.810
What is this?

01:21:16.620 --> 01:21:16.730
[Bold Santa Sooji delivering the gift]

01:21:16.730 --> 01:21:18.070
Who are you?

01:21:18.200 --> 01:21:19.540
Who are you?

01:21:19.750 --> 01:21:21.360
Who are you?

01:21:21.610 --> 01:21:24.070
[2:34 PM]

01:21:24.410 --> 01:21:24.860
[The first person
to deliver a gift — Dex!]

01:21:24.860 --> 01:21:26.170
This is seriously…

01:21:26.290 --> 01:21:27.450
Two minutes.

01:21:27.630 --> 01:21:30.150
[If I'd gone to the right place,
I would've been first.]

01:21:30.470 --> 01:21:31.810
[Oh?!]

01:21:31.990 --> 01:21:34.200
[Dex, congratulations! A special video
will be revealed for Dex,]

01:21:34.200 --> 01:21:36.420
[who delivered the first gift.]

01:21:36.680 --> 01:21:38.050
[Amazing. Amazing!]

01:21:38.330 --> 01:21:38.910
[Obtained the first-gift bonus]

01:21:38.910 --> 01:21:39.770
Director.

01:21:39.920 --> 01:21:41.230
Protein.

01:21:42.470 --> 01:21:43.690
[Who is it?]

01:21:44.600 --> 01:21:46.490
[Protein drink~?!]

01:21:46.930 --> 01:21:50.360
[The only perk that lets you see
your Manito's reaction]

01:21:50.670 --> 01:21:53.510
[Ahahaha, he got it~?]

01:21:53.890 --> 01:21:55.030
[Hehe, I knew it.]

01:21:55.030 --> 01:21:55.090
43 grams.

01:21:55.090 --> 01:21:56.060
[Protein: 43 g]

01:21:56.060 --> 01:21:56.240
I told you—he'd definitely pick
the one with the highest content.

01:21:56.240 --> 01:21:58.530
[Exactly as expected.]

01:21:58.960 --> 01:21:59.020
[Excited by the vivid reaction
to receiving the gift]

01:21:59.020 --> 01:22:01.060
Why is he so relaxed?

01:22:03.560 --> 01:22:03.680
Still, it's kind of reassuring.

01:22:03.680 --> 01:22:05.290
[A gift delivery
filled with thrill and joy!]

01:22:05.290 --> 01:22:07.350
Seeing how he reacted
when he got the gift…

01:22:07.350 --> 01:22:09.270
[Short reply: Thanks
for the protein powder.]

01:22:09.540 --> 01:22:11.030
[I just received it in my room.]

01:22:11.340 --> 01:22:13.130
[Gift status]

01:22:13.130 --> 01:22:16.060
[Gift status: Not received]

01:22:17.010 --> 01:22:18.540
[Wait—hold on.]

01:22:18.720 --> 01:22:21.800
[My Manito is totally silent~?]

01:22:22.100 --> 01:22:24.640
Where is he?
[Suddenly remembers her own Manito]

01:22:24.980 --> 01:22:26.830
[Is he…
off doing another schedule?]

01:22:26.990 --> 01:22:28.800
[Doesn't know what's important anymore~]

01:22:29.730 --> 01:22:32.010
[Ugh, the traffic is terrible…]

01:22:32.310 --> 01:22:32.320
Decaf latte.

01:22:32.320 --> 01:22:36.430
[Driving 40 minutes
to buy Sooji's favorite coffee]

01:22:36.740 --> 01:22:38.710
You know that, right, hyung…?

01:22:38.710 --> 01:22:40.750
[I don't drink coffee.]

01:22:40.960 --> 01:22:41.050
Just to buy coffee.

01:22:41.050 --> 01:22:43.510
[I've never been this desperate
just to buy coffee before…]

01:22:43.510 --> 01:22:46.510
Coming out at this hour
this is my first time in my life.

01:22:46.830 --> 01:22:48.320
[Rabbit~]

01:22:48.860 --> 01:22:50.660
[I'm not that greedy.]

01:22:50.840 --> 01:22:52.470
As long as it matches
her taste, that's enough.

01:22:52.830 --> 01:22:54.500
[As for me…]

01:22:54.710 --> 01:22:56.790
[What I'm thinking about now is—]

01:22:56.950 --> 01:22:59.300
[An unexpected gift!]

01:22:59.510 --> 01:22:59.550
[Plan 1: Rent a racetrack]

01:22:59.550 --> 01:23:01.010
I want to rent a racetrack.

01:23:01.110 --> 01:23:02.040
Then I can ride a motorcycle with him.

01:23:02.040 --> 01:23:04.360
[Plan 2: Ride motorcycles together]

01:23:04.570 --> 01:23:06.620
[Huh? The crew:
But gifts must be delivered]

01:23:06.620 --> 01:23:08.680
[without revealing your identity…]

01:23:09.080 --> 01:23:13.310
[Ah… we can't ride together?]

01:23:13.790 --> 01:23:17.480
[Will Sunghoon be able
to deliver the gift safely…?]

01:23:17.600 --> 01:23:17.710
Let's go.

01:23:17.710 --> 01:23:18.720
[The uncle finally makes a move!]

01:23:18.720 --> 01:23:18.840
[Choo pushes Plan 1: renting
a limited-edition motorcycle and track]

01:23:18.840 --> 01:23:21.130
I want to book a racetrack
and ride motorcycles with him together.

01:23:21.130 --> 01:23:21.460
[(Source: Dex socials)]

01:23:21.460 --> 01:23:23.720
If we go racing together,
it'll be amazing.

01:23:23.720 --> 01:23:24.960
[Hey, are you busy tomorrow?]

01:23:24.960 --> 01:23:25.320
[Choo pushes Plan 2:
invite an international star]

01:23:25.320 --> 01:23:26.210
I should be free.

01:23:26.210 --> 01:23:26.340
[Choo pushes Plan 3: travel abroad too?]

01:23:26.340 --> 01:23:27.880
Whether it's Japan or anywhere else,

01:23:27.880 --> 01:23:29.340
we could do a two-day-one-night trip.

01:23:29.340 --> 01:23:30.150
[Would that even work?]

01:23:31.580 --> 01:23:31.680
[Hongchul has already
been driving for 8 hours]

01:23:31.680 --> 01:23:33.950
[I don't even know if I'm a Manito
or just a chauffeur anymore.]

01:23:33.950 --> 01:23:34.320
My Manito is completely silent.

01:23:34.320 --> 01:23:35.220
[(Sooji)]

01:23:35.220 --> 01:23:36.520
[Sooji, I'm here!!!]

01:23:36.730 --> 01:23:38.150
I have to see
the reaction with my own eyes!

01:23:38.210 --> 01:23:38.350
So nervous. So nervous.

01:23:38.350 --> 01:23:40.270
[Trying to see the reaction —
but risking exposure?]

01:23:40.460 --> 01:23:41.450
Can I lose control?

01:23:41.450 --> 01:23:41.640
[Jennie's additional gift attack]

01:23:41.640 --> 01:23:42.970
How should I ambush him?

01:23:43.050 --> 01:23:43.190
I feel like I'm going to get caught.

01:23:43.190 --> 01:23:44.630
[Boldly infiltrating Dex's base]

01:23:44.890 --> 01:23:46.350
I think he's about to come out.

01:23:46.350 --> 01:23:47.890
[Run! Run!]

01:23:47.890 --> 01:23:48.620
What is this?

01:23:48.940 --> 01:23:49.760
[Did they come here before?]

01:23:49.760 --> 01:23:50.300
Did they?

01:23:50.380 --> 01:23:51.950
[Stop right there!!!]

01:23:51.950 --> 01:23:52.460
Whatever.

01:23:52.460 --> 01:23:53.930
[The distance
between the two keeps closing]

01:23:53.930 --> 01:23:55.630
He's really coming out—really.

01:23:55.630 --> 01:23:57.060
[Can she avoid Dex's radar?]

01:23:57.060 --> 01:23:58.790
[Emergency call
from Manito Club HQ]

01:23:58.790 --> 01:23:59.910
We need to go to HQ.

01:24:00.070 --> 01:24:02.110
Move, move.

01:24:02.240 --> 01:24:03.100
Who's going to show up?

01:24:03.100 --> 01:24:03.920
Oh wow.

01:24:03.920 --> 01:24:04.220
[Manito Club members finally meet]

01:24:04.220 --> 01:24:05.290
No. No.

01:24:05.760 --> 01:24:07.110
Hello.

01:24:07.200 --> 01:24:07.220
Everyone's here.

01:24:07.220 --> 01:24:09.100
[A warm, cheerful atmosphere]

01:24:10.010 --> 01:24:11.390
[That's what we thought… ]

01:24:11.690 --> 01:24:13.170
[Say hello—this is Rabbit hyung.]

01:24:13.400 --> 01:24:14.500
[No, no…]

01:24:14.500 --> 01:24:15.160
Not Rabbit.

01:24:15.180 --> 01:24:15.610
[Raccoon Dog!]

01:24:16.450 --> 01:24:16.560
Jennie, why are you so shocked?

01:24:16.560 --> 01:24:18.490
[Jennie, why are you reacting like that?]

01:24:18.660 --> 01:24:20.420
[Please don't pay attention to me…]

01:24:20.420 --> 01:24:20.510
What? I don't know.

01:24:20.510 --> 01:24:21.820
[A duel to protect one's identity]

01:24:21.820 --> 01:24:23.400
No, no, no.

01:24:23.770 --> 01:24:24.970
[Is it exposed?]

01:24:24.970 --> 01:24:25.950
[Lee Sooji]

01:24:25.950 --> 01:24:26.060
[A total mess of disguises]

01:24:26.060 --> 01:24:26.930
Lee Sooji.

01:24:26.930 --> 01:24:28.410
[At this rate… will this even work…?]

01:24:28.490 --> 01:24:28.630
A group activity for Secret Manito.

01:24:28.630 --> 01:24:31.360
[A new mission is given to them]

01:24:31.360 --> 01:24:33.310
[HQ: Your Secret Manito]

01:24:33.310 --> 01:24:34.730
[HQ: is????]

01:24:34.730 --> 01:24:36.570
[Beyond imagination — the identities of the Secret Manito…]

01:24:36.570 --> 01:24:37.680
Really?

01:24:39.910 --> 01:24:41.840
It feels like someone just came in.

01:24:42.770 --> 01:24:43.990
What is this?

01:24:45.300 --> 01:24:45.870
That's amazing.